(1. PURPOSE) Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
(Passport Security is a full-stack information system for online passport services. The) Tj
0 -13 Td
(application supports applicant registration, email verification, account identity verification,) Tj
0 -13 Td
(passport application submission, staff review, passport issuance, and admin management. The) Tj
0 -13 Td
(system is designed as a controlled workflow where an applicant cannot submit a passport) Tj
0 -13 Td
(application until their account has been verified.) Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
