0 -13 Td
(2. **Express backend** for API routes, authentication, validation, business rules, and database) Tj
0 -13 Td
(access.) Tj
0 -13 Td
(3. **Supabase PostgreSQL and Storage** for persistent data and uploaded files.) Tj
0 -13 Td
(4. **Python OCR/AI services** for account document extraction and passport document extraction.) Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
